nodes.text: A moon in the galaxy was once colonized by the Geonosian species. Long after the moon had been abandoned, during the Imperial Era, antiques dealer Antron Bach went into hiding on the moon with a cache of Jedi artifacts he had been entrusted with by Jedi Master Uvell. Bach lived there alone until Corellian Resistance member Miru Nadrinakar crash-landed on the moon.
